snippet.title: Star Conflict: Shrike
snippet.description:
The Shrike was created at the Boson Shipyard, one of the IDR shipyards. Business angels from Undock Unlimited financed the development. The configuration of the ship was optimized with the help of Ariadne. With the use of cutting-edge technology, the engineers were able to build one of the best modern cover ships.

Official website: https://star-conflict.com
Twitch channel: https://www.twitch.tv/starconflicten 

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/StarConflict/ 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/starconflicten 
Steam: http://steamcommunity.com/app/212070
